hopobject.body: In a meeting drugtestyourteen.com coupon WILL: Young people, young people are not going to sign up if they can do elementary arithmetic, which they can. Why indeed not suspend the individual mandate? Because the law doesn’t provide it? The law means nothing to these people. And by the way, this is why Cokie, this is going to affect the immigration debate. Because the House Republicans are going to say, no matter what we write in the law, this administration will waive any provision it doesn’t like.
